It has an impressive, international team of tutors at its disposal and the quality of the designers they educate is very high.  The DNA of Design Academy Eindhoven can be described as conceptual, authentic, creative, flexible, free, passionate and curious.    Design Academy Eindhoven is always looking for excellence and intends to be the most authentic, creative, and innovative academy in the world; a professional organisation and educational institution that produces top design talent.
